snippet.title: I made a Multiplayer RTS Game
snippet.description:
Conquela is a multiplayer real-time strategy game where you collect resources, build structures and destroy your enemy's castle. it's finally out! :D oh, and its FREEE!!!
you can download from:
itch: https://wingdinghq.itch.io/conquela

gamejolt: https://gamejolt.com/games/conquela/868367

https://discord.gg/JQzpB2gnMA

devlog: https://wingdinghq.itch.io/conquela/devlog/679598/multiplayer-beta-conquela-090

Conquela is an indie game which this video is a devlog of. gamedev or game dev or game development. The game is out on itch.io and gamejolt, it is a multiplayer strategy game also known as rts or real time strategy.
